          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Small Business Investment Opportunity Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Small Business Investment Act of 1958 to increase the maximum amount of outstanding leverage (i.e., borrowing power) made available to any licensed small business investment company from $150 million to $175 million.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-03-08T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
